<seg rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">
短歌集　日まはり<lb />
</seg><seg rend="jisage_11" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 11em">
わが跫音<lb />
路をうつわが杖の音<lb />
われは聴く<lb />
わが生の音づれ<lb />
